<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Mapa miestnosti</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #111827;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    p { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #9ca3af; }
    .room-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .screen {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #374151;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.1s, box-shadow 0.1s, background 0.1s;
    }
    .screen-title { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .status { font-size: 14px; }
    .free { background: #064e3b; }
    .occupied { background: #7f1d1d; cursor: not-allowed; }
    .screen:hover:not(.occupied) {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Mapa miestnosti</h1>
  <p>Vyber si obrazovku, na ktorú sa pripojíš. Každá môže mať len jedného účastníka.</p>

  <div class="room-grid">
    <div class="screen" data-screen="screen1">
      <div class="screen-title">Obrazovka 1</div>
      <div class="status">Načítavam...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="screen" data-screen="screen2">
      <div class="screen-title">Obrazovka 2</div>
      <div class="status">Načítavam...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="screen" data-screen="screen3">
      <div class="screen-title">Obrazovka 3</div>
      <div class="status">Načítavam...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="screen" data-screen="screen4">
      <div class="screen-title">Obrazovka 4 (zdieľanie)</div>
      <div class="status">Načítavam...</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/peerjs@1.5.2/dist/peerjs.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/map.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
